OL,3,CWhat could the budget mean for Wales?
OL,5,FThe UK Government Budget to be set out
OL,6,Fby Jeremy Hunt on Wednesday will be
OL,7,Fone of the most politically important
OL,8,Fin recent years: it could be the last
OL,9,Fbefore the next UK General Election
OL,10,Fand will certainly set out dividing
OL,11,Flines for that election whenever it
OL,12,Fcomes.
OL,14,FFor months the Chancellor of the
OL,15,FExchequer and other senior figures
OL,16,Fhave hinted that voters can expect tax
OL,17,Fcuts; Jeremy Hunt has repeatedly said
OL,18,Fthat his preference is to "lighten the
OL,19,Ftax burden" rather than increase
OL,20,Fspending.
