OL,3,CWhat could the budget mean for Wales?
OL,5,FIt's widely reported that he is
OL,6,Flooking at cutting income tax or
OL,7,Fnational insurance but that rising
OL,8,Fdebt levels are making that difficult.
OL,10,FSo what sort of changes might we see
OL,11,Fon Wednesday and how might those
OL,12,Fchanges affect people living and
OL,13,Fworking here in Wales?
OL,15,FIncome tax cut for low or middle
OL,16,Fearners
OL,18,FA 1 or 2% cut to the basic, or 20%
OL,19,Frate, of income tax or a similar cut
OL,20,Fto national insurance contributions
OL,21,Fseems almost certain.
