OL,3,CWhat could the budget mean for Wales?
OL,5,FIncome tax thresholds - the amount of
OL,6,Fincome you have to earn before you
OL,7,Fbegin paying different rates of tax -
OL,8,Fhave been frozen since the Spring
OL,9,FBudget of 2021, when Rishi Sunak was
OL,10,FChancellor, to save money.
OL,12,FBut inflation means that many more
OL,13,Fpeople are finding themselves in
OL,14,Fhigher tax brackets with experts
OL,15,Festimating that the effect of frozen
OL,16,Fthresholds is the equivalent of an
OL,17,Fincrease in basic rate income tax of
OL,18,F6%.
