OL,5,FJeremy Hunt considered cutting it in
OL,6,Fthe Autumn statement but decided
OL,7,Fagainst it. It would be popular with
OL,8,Fmany Conservative voters but could
OL,9,Fleave him facing accusations of
OL,10,Ffavouring the better-off.
