OL,3,CWhat could the budget mean for Wales?
OL,5,FThe Chancellor is said to be cutting a
OL,6,Ftax relief scheme for owners of
OL,7,Fproperties that are rented out to
OL,8,Fholidaymakers. Under the Furnished
OL,9,FHoliday Lets regime, there are tax
OL,10,Freliefs for furnishing holiday
OL,11,Fproperties and reductions in capital
OL,12,Fgains tax on properties that are
OL,13,Favailable for holiday letting for at
OL,14,Fleast 210 days a year.
OL,16,FAccording to the Sunday Times,
OL,17,Fscrapping these tax reliefs could
OL,18,Fbring the Treasury around #300m a year.
